title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>An element <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a]]></fr:tex> of a pointed dcpo <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is called <fr:em>non-negatively generated</fr:em> when <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[a \sqsubseteq  \bigsqcup _{\lnot {\mathopen {}\left (a=\bot \right )\mathclose {}}}a]]></fr:tex> holds.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
